title: Should we increase the payments for exekias, nicholas, natimuril and buradorii?
body:
Proposed changes from FC3 to FC4:
Increase exekias payment from $3000 to $4000 
Increase nicholas payment from $1500 to $2000
Increase nati payment from $500 to $1000
Increase buradorii payment from $500 to $1000

Context:
Blogpost by Jango with the proposal explained:
